# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and on checkout. The build nodes are
# Linux and the verify scripts are bash; a CRLF shebang or CRLF-terminated
# source must never reach them.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.rs text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.wgsl text eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be line-ending normalized or diffed as text.
*.png binary
